    {
      "id": 1782022196063,
      "type": "columns-2",
      "props": {
        "title": "",
        "leftTitle": "",
        "leftContent": "",
        "leftImage": "https://bvtxfphktypdqmlnveqf.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/assets/35ab846e-0764-498b-b1f8-7d2cf27d85a5/web-1782023807155-ChatGPT-Image-Jun-21-2026-04_36_31-PM.png",
        "rightTitle": "<span style=\"font-size: 32px;\">CRM (Customer Relationship Management)</span>",
        "rightContent": "<span><span><p style=\"font-size: 19px; text-align: justify;\">A CRM (Customer Relationship Management) system is one of the most valuable tools a growing business can implement. Many businesses still rely on spreadsheets, notebooks, email inboxes, and memory to manage customer relationships, leads, quotes, and follow-ups. While this may work in the early stages, it quickly becomes difficult to maintain consistency, resulting in missed opportunities, forgotten follow-ups, and lost revenue.<br><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; text-align: justify;\">The Gr8 Result CRM is designed to centralise every customer interaction in one easy-to-manage platform. Every lead, customer enquiry, quote, phone call, email, SMS conversation, task, and appointment can be stored and tracked from a single dashboard. This gives business owners and their teams complete visibility over their sales pipeline, ensuring no lead falls through the cracks and every opportunity is followed up at the right time.<br><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; text-align: justify;\">One of the biggest advantages of the Gr8 Result CRM is automation. Instead of manually chasing leads, setting reminders, or sending follow-up emails, the system can automate these tasks for you. Automated workflows, email campaigns, SMS reminders, and task scheduling help businesses respond faster, nurture prospects more effectively, and convert more enquiries into paying customers. The result is increased efficiency, improved customer experiences, and significantly higher conversion rates.<br><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; text-align: justify;\">For businesses that have never used a CRM before, the impact can be immediate. Teams become more organised, communication improves, and management gains real-time visibility into sales performance. Business owners can instantly see where leads are coming from, which team members are performing best, which marketing campaigns are generating results, and where opportunities are being lost. This level of insight allows businesses to make smarter decisions based on real data rather than guesswork.<br><br>Unlike traditional CRM systems that can be complex and difficult to implement, the Gr8 Result CRM has been built with simplicity and usability in mind. Its intuitive interface allows businesses to get up and running quickly while still providing the powerful tools needed to scale. Whether you're a small business looking to improve lead management or a growing company needing advanced automation and reporting, the Gr8 Result CRM provides the foundation for sustainable growth.<br><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; text-align: justify;\"><span><span><span><span><span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">Ultimately, businesses that use a CRM close more sales, deliver better customer service, and operate more efficiently than those that don't. The Gr8 Result CRM gives businesses the tools, automation, and visibility they need to turn more enquiries into customers, retain those customers for longer, and create predictable, scalable growth.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p></span></span>",
        "rightImage": "",
        "ratio": "60-40",
