        "items": [
          {
            "id": "8ff27e7f-e8ca-4f4a-b79b-9e7c0a5eefe3",
            "text": "We switched over to Gr8 Result about six months ago and we were able to cut our subscrptions tool stack from 9 apps to 1. Our team saves over 12 hours a week and our lead-to-close rate is up 40%.",
            "author": "David Waite",
            "role": "CEO, Waite and Sea Health &amp; Fitness",
            "rating": 5,
            "avatarUrl": "https://bvtxfphktypdqmlnveqf.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/assets/35ab846e-0764-498b-b1f8-7d2cf27d85a5/web-1779061738959-default-avatar.png",
            "avatarAssetId": "asset:35ab846e-0764-498b-b1f8-7d2cf27d85a5/web-1779061738959-default-avatar.png"
          },
          {
            "id": "225b5cab-fe01-4c8d-bc89-f68aaed376cf",
            "text": "The CRM and email automation alone are worth the price. But the AI phone system? That's what blew our team away. We're handling 3x— the leads without adding headcount.",
            "author": "Josh Rohde",
            "role": "Managing Director, Truline Cabinets.",
            "rating": 5,
            "avatarUrl": "https://bvtxfphktypdqmlnveqf.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/assets/35ab846e-0764-498b-b1f8-7d2cf27d85a5/web-1781725153882-ChatGPT-Image-Jun-17--2026--02_19_06-PM.png",
            "avatarAssetId": "asset:35ab846e-0764-498b-b1f8-7d2cf27d85a5/web-1781725153882-ChatGPT-Image-Jun-17--2026--02_19_06-PM.png"
          },
          {
            "id": "ef6e9cdc-a050-45c6-8d21-c70bb86cf89f",
            "text": "Their onboarding team had us live in under just a few days. The website builder replaced our old drag-and-drop tool and the AI Funnel Builder tool is so quick and easy to use.",
            "author": "Sarah Reid",
            "role": "Co-Founder, operations, Elan Interiors",
            "rating": 5,
            "avatarUrl": "https://i.pravatar.cc/80?img=31",
            "avatarAssetId": "32b6d482-d7e4-409e-b448-896a956fb7f2"
          },
          {
            "id": "92c11cc1-150a-4b49-801e-3e1f8578b8cd",
            "text": "I've tried so many other all-in-one platforms. Gr8 Result is the first one that doesn't sacrifice depth for breadth and ease of use. It's been on of the best decision we made this year.",
            "author": "Tom Hargreaves",
            "role": "Operations Manager, Sprint Media",
            "rating": 5,
